6
00:00:17,252 --> 00:00:20,594
on the topic of escape rooms, and specifically,

7
00:00:20,594 --> 00:00:24,076
why escape rooms are so great for teaching game design

8
00:00:24,076 --> 00:00:26,338
basics to new students.

9
00:00:26,338 --> 00:00:30,681
So first, a little bit about me.

10
00:00:30,681 --> 00:00:32,702
I am a professor at Northeastern University,

11
00:00:32,702 --> 00:00:36,004
where I teach fundamentals of game design and other classes.

12
00:00:36,822 --> 00:00:43,488
Additionally, I am a consultant in my normal work where I do games for Impact, also known as Serious Games.

13
